<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div xml:id="PN302">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>veṭivēy koḷvatu pōla vōṭit</l>
<l>tāvu pukaḷu māvē pūvē</l>
<l>viḷaṅkiḻai makaḷir kūntaṟ koṇṭa</l>
<l>narantap palkāḻk kōtai cuṟṟiya</l>
<l>vaitamai pāṇi vaṇarkōṭṭuc cīṟiyāḻk</l>
<l>kaivār narampiṉ pāṇark kōkkiya</l>
<l>nirampā viyalpiṟ karampaic cīṟūr</l>
<l>nōkkiṉarc cekukkuṅ kāḷai yūkki</l>
<l>vēli ṉaṭṭa kaḷiṟupeyart teṇṇiṉ</l>
<l>viṇṇivar vicumpiṉ mīṉun</l>
<l>taṇpeya luṟaiyu muṟaiyāṟ ṟāvē.</l>
</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>Like the take of cracking bamboos run,</l>
<l>leap [and] jump the horses. The flowers,</l>
<l>the are taken for the tresses of girls with shining jewels.</l>
<l>Little villages in the waste-land of an insufficient quality</l>
<l>are offered to bards with strings tuned by hand</l>
<l>on little lutes with curved necks [and] a wonderfully suited beat</l>
<l>that wore many-strand garlands of bitter orange.</l>
<l>The young man who will destroy those who look at [them],</l>
<l>if you count again the elephants he killed with [his] spear,</l>
<l>they cannot match [in number] the stars in the sky</l>
<l>wandering across the firmament and the drops of cool rain.</l>
</lg>
    </div>
